## Files Found

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `docs/extensions.md` | Full extension API reference |
| `docs/sdk.md` | Programmatic SDK usage |
| `docs/packages.md` | Pi package distribution format |
| `examples/extensions/hello.ts` | Minimal tool registration |
| `examples/extensions/tools.ts` | Tool config UI command |
| `examples/extensions/commands.ts` | Command listing |
| `examples/extensions/todo.ts` | Stateful tool + TUI component |
| `examples/extensions/dynamic-tools.ts` | Runtime tool registration |
| `examples/extensions/question.ts` | Interactive custom UI tool |
| `examples/extensions/subagent/` | Multi-file extension (agent discovery) |
| `examples/extensions/plan-mode/` | Multi-file with utils |
| `examples/extensions/with-deps/` | Extension with npm deps |
| `examples/extensions/sandbox/` | Built-in tool override |
